OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency has criticised
OL,7,Fwater companies over their
OL,8,F"unacceptable" performance on sewage
OL,9,Fspills last year.
OL,11,FThe regulator said five out of nine
OL,12,Fcompanies in England were rated as
OL,13,F"requiring improvement" in its annual
OL,14,Freport released on Tuesday.
OL,16,FThis included Thames Water, the UK's
OL,17,Fbiggest water supplier, which has been
OL,18,Funder fire in recent months over
OL,19,Fpollution and financial woes.
