OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FIt comes as the sector faces a
OL,7,Fnational crisis after years of under-
OL,8,Finvestment by the privately-run firms
OL,9,Fcombined with ageing water
OL,10,Finfrastructure a growing population
OL,11,Fand wetter conditions caused by
OL,12,Fclimate change.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency said there were
OL,15,F47 serious pollution incidents last
OL,16,Fyear ` up from 44 in 2022.
OL,18,FFour companies ` Thames Water,
OL,19,FSouthern Water, Anglian Water and
OL,20,FYorkshire Water ` caused 90% of those
OL,21,Fincidents, it added.
