OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FAlan Lovell, chairman of the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency, said: "This is
OL,8,Funacceptable."
OL,10,F"My over-riding sense is one of
OL,11,Ffrustration and disappointment," he
OL,12,Fadded. "The results we see are, yet
OL,13,Fagain, simply not good enough."
OL,15,FThe annual report said there was a
OL,16,F"small improvement" in environmental
OL,17,Fprotection among some firms and that
OL,18,FSevern Trent, Wessex Water and United
OL,19,FUtilities performed well.
