OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FBut the regulator said the majority
OL,7,Fare not getting the basics right, such
OL,8,Fas minimising pollution incidents and
OL,9,Fcomplying with permits.
OL,11,FMr Lovell said the culture within some
OL,12,Ffirms "can also perpetuate poor
OL,13,Fpractices" and warned that the
OL,14,Fregulator will not take "bad weather"
OL,15,Fas an excuse for poor environmental
OL,16,Fperformance.
