OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FHe said: "Some simply do not
OL,7,Funderstand the root cause of their
OL,8,Fproblems and incidents are not
OL,9,Freported in a timely manner ` this is
OL,10,Fvital for improving transparency and
OL,11,Ftrust across this sector.
OL,13,F"We know that with a changing climate,
OL,14,Fthe country is going to experience
OL,15,Fmore extreme weather patterns,
OL,16,Fincreased rainfall and more rapid
OL,17,Fdrought.
OL,19,F"Water companies must ensure that
OL,20,Fassets are resilient enough to
OL,21,Fwithstand these challenges."
