OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,FFor its part, the Environment Agency
OL,7,Fsaid it would introduce a tougher
OL,8,Fregulatory approach.
OL,10,FIt outlined plans for recruiting 500
OL,11,Fadditional staff, investing in digital
OL,12,Fsystems, increasing enforcement
OL,13,Factivity and quadrupling the number of
OL,14,Fwater company inspections to 4,000
OL,15,Fbefore April next year.
OL,17,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed
OL,18,Fcalled the findings "shocking".
