OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,F"For too long, water companies have
OL,7,Fpumped record levels of sewage into
OL,8,Four rivers, lakes and seas. This
OL,9,FGovernment will never let this happen
OL,10,Fagain."
OL,12,FThe new Government has announced plans
OL,13,Fto crack down on water firms,
OL,14,Fincluding tougher fines for pollution
OL,15,Fincidents and ensuring money is
OL,16,Finvested into infrastructure rather
OL,17,Fthan paid out in bonuses.
