OL,7,Foutline further legislation to
OL,8,Ffundamentally transform our water
OL,9,Findustry and restore our rivers, lakes
OL,10,Fand seas to good health," Mr Reed
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Thames Water said:
OL,14,F"Protecting the environment is
OL,15,Ffundamental to what we do and we
OL,16,Frecognise our performance in
OL,17,Fpreventing pollutions is still not
OL,18,Fgood enough.
