OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,F"Our region has experienced the
OL,7,Fwettest winter since records began,
OL,8,Fresulting in exceptionally high
OL,9,Fgroundwater and river levels. This has
OL,10,Fat times overwhelmed our sewer system
OL,11,Fand has led to discharges into rivers.
OL,13,F"More investment is needed across the
OL,14,Fentire sector, as infrastructure ages
OL,15,Fand demand on it increases. That's why
OL,16,Fwe've asked for increased investment
OL,17,Fin the next regulatory cycle between
OL,18,F2025-2030 so we can improve outcomes
OL,19,Ffor customers, and the environment.
