OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,F"Our River Health Plan highlights our
OL,7,Fambition to deliver these changes. We
OL,8,Fare upgrading 250 of our sewage
OL,9,Ftreatment works to reduce the number
OL,10,Fof storm discharges to protect the
OL,11,Fenvironment and eliminate the risk of
OL,12,Fincidents in the future."
OL,14,FJohn Penicud, Southern Water's
OL,15,FDirector for Wastewater Operations,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Despite the wettest Winter on
OL,17,Frecord we've reduced pollutions by 35%
OL,18,Fand we've been given a two-star EPA
OL,19,Frating accordingly.
