OL,3,CWater firms' performance on sewage
OL,4,Cspills 'unacceptable', regulator says
OL,6,F"Despite our Turnaround Plan
OL,7,Fdemonstrating strong progress, the
OL,8,Fnumber of serious pollutions is
OL,9,Funacceptable, and we accept that there
OL,10,Fis a lot more to do as we urgently
OL,11,Fwork to achieve a three-star rating.
OL,13,F"To help us on this journey we are
OL,14,Fcontinuing to make improvements and
OL,15,Finnovations. One example is the
OL,16,Fintroduction of 22,000 radar devices
OL,17,Fin manholes across our 45,000km sewer
OL,18,Fnetwork which will help us proactively
OL,19,Fdetect issues before they become
OL,20,Fpollutions."
